  <ol>
    <li id="fn:1">
      <p><a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/242606/number-of-active-twitter-users-in-selected-countries/">Statista</a>, ref. abril de 2020 <a href="#fnref:1" class="reversefootnote">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
